author: Ed Kilgore
title: Wisconsin Court Reinstates Tuesday’s Mid-Pandemic Primary
description: After intense gubernatorial and legislative conflict and multiple appeals, it looks like Republicans will get the low-turnout election they wanted.
content: In a decision that might have been considered shocking coming from anywhere other than the conservative majority in hyper-polarized Wisconsin, that states Supreme Court granted a petition from Republican legislators to overrule the Democratic governors effort… [+4393 chars]
